---
<section class="v2-about" id="about">
  <div class="v2-about-inner">
    <!-- 美琪老師照片 -->
    <div class="v2-about-img-wrap">
      <img src="/images/v2-about.jpg" alt="美琪老師 - 六號美容美學專業美容師" class="v2-about-img" />
    </div>

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="v2-about-text">
      <h2 class="v2-about-title">關於美琪老師</h2>
      <p class="v2-about-body">
        文案 placeholder — 客戶後補。美琪老師從事美容護理工作已逾二十年，累積了豐富的實務經驗。她專注於傾聽每一位顧客的肌膚需求，從清粉刺到深層護理，皆以細膩手法與溫和態度完成。工作室採全預約制，確保每位客人都能獲得安心、專屬的服務時光。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .v2-about {
    background: var(--v2-light-bg);
    padding: 100px 5vw 120px;
  }
  .v2-about-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .v2-about-img-wrap {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  .v2-about-img-wrap.visible {
    animation: v2-fade-in-up 0.9s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .v2-about-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    filter: brightness(1.02);
  }
  .v2-about-text {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  .v2-about-text.visible {
    animation: v2-fade-in-up 0.9s ease-out 0.15s forwards;
  }
  .v2-about-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--v2-text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .v2-about-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--v2-muted-text);
  }
  @keyframes v2-fade-in-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .v2-about {
      padding: 72px 6vw 88px;
    }
    .v2-about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .v2-about-img-wrap {
      max-width: 320px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function() {
    var section = document.querySelector('.v2-about');
    if (!section) return;
    var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries) {
      entries.forEach(function(entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          section.querySelector('.v2-about-img-wrap').classList.add('visible');
          section.querySelector('.v2-about-text').classList.add('visible');
          observer.disconnect();
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });
    observer.observe(section);
  })();
</script>
